
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {{platformName}}!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100%;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #334155;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #047857 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #1e293b;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: #475569;
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .highlight-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #166534;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .highlight-box p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #166534;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #059669;
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 10px 20px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #047857;
        }
        .cta-button.secondary {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #059669;
            border: 2px solid #059669;
        }
        .cta-button.secondary:hover {
            background-color: #059669;
            color: white;
        }
        .steps {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .step {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .step-number {
            background-color: #059669;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 15px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .step-content h4 {
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            color: #1e293b;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .step-content p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .info-box h4 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #92400e;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .info-box ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #92400e;
        }
        .info-box li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .footer h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #1e293b;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer .copyright {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }
        .support-link {
            color: #059669;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .support-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to {{platformName}}!</h1>
            <p>Your seller account has been approved</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Dear {{sellerName}},
            </div>

            <div class="message">
                Congratulations! We're excited to inform you that your seller account has been <strong>approved</strong> and you can now start selling on {{platformName}}.
            </div>

            {{#if businessName}}
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <h3>Your Store Details</h3>
                <p><strong>Store Name:</strong> {{businessName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{sellerEmail}}</p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color: #059669; font-weight: bold;">Approved ✓</span></p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <h3 style="color: #1e293b; margin: 30px 0 20px 0; font-size: 20px; border-bottom: 2px solid #059669; padding-bottom: 8px;">
                Next Steps to Get Started
            </h3>

            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h4>Access Your Dashboard</h4>
                        <p>Log in to your seller dashboard to complete your profile and store setup if not completed yet.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h4>Upload Your Products</h4>
                        <p>Start adding your products with high-quality images, detailed descriptions and other informations.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h4>📋 Important Reminders</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Complete your store profile within 7 days to maintain active status</li>
                    <li>Follow our seller guidelines to ensure smooth operations</li>
                    <li>Upload at least 5 products to start appearing in search results</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="message">
                We're here to support your success every step of the way. If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <h3>Welcome to the {{platformName}}</h3>
            <p>
                Need help? Contact us at 
                <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" class="support-link">{{supportEmail}}</a>
            </p>
            
            <div class="copyright">
                <p>© {{currentYear}} {{platformName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
